%p.article-title= "Hi #{@guest.first_name.capitalize},"
%p.article-content= "Sorry, but #{@host.first_name.capitalize} is unavailable on the dates you have booked, although they would be happy to be hired or enquired again later!"
- if @booking.response_message.present?
  %p.article-content= "#{@host.first_name.capitalize} has also included the following message:"
  %p.article-content
    %strong= @booking.response_message

%p.article-content.email-message-reply
  %strong= link_to 'Reply to this message', mailbox_messages_url(@booking.mailbox), style: 'color:#444444;'

%p.article-content
  %i HomeStay Title:
  = @homestay.title.capitalize
  %br
  %strong
    %i Date requested:
    from
    = @booking.check_in_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)
    to
    = @booking.check_out_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)

%p.article-content
  %strong Click 
  = link_to 'here', my_account_url
  %strong to Search and Enquire with more fantastic HomeStays in your Postcode.

%p.article-content
  %strong
    If you can’t find a suitable HomeStay, and you need it within 2 weeks, please contact us via email at 
    info@pethomestay.com and we will do our best to assist you.

%p.article-content Many thanks!
%p.article-content The PetHomeStay Team
